{"title":"Found: The wild Loris Klin concept bike hints at a fully integrated bikepacking future","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/09/14/found-the-wild-loris-klin-concept-bike-hints-at-a-fully-integrated-bikepacking-future/","date":1631649307000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152022/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-8-800x534.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs%3Adevice%2Frscb28-1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\"><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-271625\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>What does the future of bikepacking look like? Well, if Loris’ Project Klin is any indication, it will be a lot more integrated. As their entry for the 2021 Concours de Machines, Loris took this year’s bikepacking theme and truly ran with it, coming up with this incredible concept bike in the process.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152028/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-10.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152028/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-10.jpg\" alt=\"Loris Klin bikepacking concept bike\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152028/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-10.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152028/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-10-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152028/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-10-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152028/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-10-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152028/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-10-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152028/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-10-1536x1025.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152028/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-10.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152028/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-10.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152028/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-10-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152028/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-10-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152028/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-10-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152028/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-10-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152028/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-10-1536x1025.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>While the bikepacking theme is fairly straight forward, there were <a href=\"https://www.associationartisansducycle.com/concours-2020-en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">quite a few requirements for each entry</a>. Basically, you needed to create a hand built bike with enough storage to be totally self sufficient, for 2-3 days. That includes the ability to store or generate your own electricity, boil water, leave no trace, contact rescue, follow GPS tracks, etc. You know, basically what everyone should be able to do on a bikepacking trip—although the requirements continue with details like “the bike must fit in a 1200mm long and 900mm high suitcase or bag, and minimise the width” to follow the SNCF French train policy for a car-free journey.</p><p>All of this is to say that these bikes must be able to actually be used in addition to their incredible looks.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11.jpg\" alt=\"Loris Klin bike packing mountain bike\" width=\"2245\" height=\"1456\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11.jpg 2245w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11-297x193.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11-800x519.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11-120x78.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11-768x498.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11-1536x996.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11-2048x1328.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2245px) 100vw, 2245px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11.jpg 2245w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11-297x193.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11-800x519.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11-120x78.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11-768x498.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11-1536x996.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152031/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-11-2048x1328.jpg 2048w\"></a></p><p>Loris says they realize that most people still only bikepack a few times a year, so they wanted to create a bike that would be fun to ride year-long without the luggage. So they opted for a 27.5+ platform with modern geometry and short chainstays.</p><p>The gorgeous frame is made from carbon fiber and features a one-piece fork/stem/bar up front that has quite a unique headtube assembly. The frame is actually disconnected between the top tube and down tube—it isn’t until the fork is installed and the steerer tube is slid through the assembly and tightened that the whole front end comes together. That carbon fork also includes the addition of Linen fiber to help absorb vibrations.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152015/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-6.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152015/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-6.jpg\" alt=\"Loris Klin head tube\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1336\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152015/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-6.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152015/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-6-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152015/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-6-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152015/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-6-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152015/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-6-768x513.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152015/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-6-1536x1026.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152015/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-6.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152015/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-6.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152015/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-6-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152015/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-6-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152015/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-6-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152015/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-6-768x513.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152015/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-6-1536x1026.jpg 1536w\"></a><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152000/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152000/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-1.jpg\" alt=\"Loris Klin battery pack\" width=\"782\" height=\"692\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152000/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-1.jpg 782w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152000/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-1-297x263.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152000/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-1-120x106.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152000/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-1-768x680.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 782px) 100vw, 782px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152000/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-1.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152000/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-1.jpg 782w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152000/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-1-297x263.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152000/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-1-120x106.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152000/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-1-768x680.jpg 768w\"></a></p><p>It seems like everywhere you look on the Klin there are hidden details that make it even more impressive. Like the integrated battery packs that were completely made in house by Loris. The battery packs not only store inside the steerer tube, but offer a mount for a Garmin GPS unit, which can then be plugged in directly to the battery. And since the steerer doesn’t turn with the bars, the computer is always still, making it easier to read and follow.</p><p>Lights are a requirement of the competition, and the Klin features a 1600 lumen KLAMP light that’s mounted under the fork and connected to the battery. There’s also a rechargeable Sigma rear light, which can be recharged by the battery pack when plugged in.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152009/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152009/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-4.jpg\" alt=\"Loris Klin components\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1061\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/14152009/Loris-Klin-bikepacking-concept-bike-handmade-Concourse-de-Machines-4.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.